        content: "**`@layer`** organizează specificitatea în straturi (layere), prevenind conflicte:\n\n```css\n/* Declara ordinea layerelor (prioritate crescatoare) */\n@layer reset, base, components, utilities;\n\n/* Reset — specificitate minimă */\n@layer reset {\n  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  :where(ul, ol) { list-style: none; padding: 0; }\n}\n\n/* Stiluri de baza */\n@layer base {\n  body {\n    font-family: var(--font-sans);\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    background: var(--bg-primary);\n  }\n  h1 { font-size: var(--text-2xl); }\n}\n\n/* Componente */\n@layer components {\n  .btn {\n    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);\n    border-radius: var(--radius-md);\n  }\n  .card {\n    background: var(--bg-secondary);\n    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n    padding: var(--space-4);\n  }\n}\n\n/* Utilities — cel mai mare priority */\n@layer utilities {\n  .hidden { display: none !important; }\n  .sr-only { position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0,0,0,0); }\n  .mt-4 { margin-top: var(--space-4); }\n}\n\n/* Code outside layers = highest priority (beats all layers) */\n.override { color: red; } /* Bate utilities */\n```"
